description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国安徽省妇女儿童工作者组成的人民团体，是中华全国妇女联合会的地方组织，接受中国共产党安徽省委员会的领导。
description.en: A people's organization composed of women and children workers in Anhui Province, People's Republic of China. It is a local organization of the All-China Women's Federation and is under the leadership of the Anhui Provincial Committee of the Communist Party of China.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国的全国性妇女组织，是安徽省妇女联合会的上级机构。
description.en: The national women's organization of the People's Republic of China, and the superior body of the Anhui Provincial Women's Federation.

description.zh-cn: 中国的一种社会组织形式，安徽省妇女联合会属于此类组织。
description.en: A form of social organization in China, to which the Anhui Provincial Women's Federation belongs.

nodes.id: 中国共产党安徽省委员会

zh-cn: 中国共产党安徽省委员会
en: Anhui Provincial Committee of the Communist Party of China

description.zh-cn: 中国共产党在安徽省的领导机关，领导安徽省妇女联合会的工作。
description.en: The leading body of the Communist Party of China in Anhui Province, which leads the work of the Anhui Provincial Women's Federation.

description.zh-cn: 安徽省妇女联合会是中华全国妇女联合会的地方组织。
description.en: The Anhui Provincial Women's Federation is a local organization of the All-China Women's Federation.

description.en: The Anhui Provincial Women's Federation is under the leadership of the Anhui Provincial Committee of the Communist Party of China.

description.zh-cn: 安徽省妇女联合会是中华人民共和国安徽省妇女儿童工作者组成的人民团体。
